1. *Razumeli* smo vaš zahtev. (We understood your request.)
2. Da li ste *razumeli* uputstva? (Did you understand the instructions?)
3. Oni nisu *razumeli* poruku. (They didn't understand the message.)
4. Nismo baš najbolje *razumeli* taj deo zadatka. (We didn't quite understand that part of the task.)
5. *Razumeli* smo se bez reči. (We understood each other without words.)
6. Molim vas, da li biste mogli da mi *razumete* situaciju? (Could you please understand my situation?)
7. Ja nikada ne bih mogao da *razumem* zašto ljudi to rade. (I could never understand why people do that.)
8. Kada sam *razumeo* koliko je važno, počeo sam ozbiljno da radim na tome. (When I understood how important it was, I started working on it seriously.)
9. Svi smo *razumeli* da se nešto čudno dešava. (We all understood that something strange was happening.)
10. *Razumeli* bismo vašu frustraciju da smo u istoj situaciji. (We would understand your frustration if we were in the same situation.)